snippet.title: Control and Crafting - An Elaborate History of Chess - DevLog 2
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1255020/An_Elaborate_History_of_Chess/

In this dev log we cover some of the things that should make your units easier to control over time in An Elaborate History of Chess. And then to stay on track, we cover the inventory and crafting!

Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/f2hdFN6
Check out our last game Paper Pirates: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1234220/Paper_Pirates/

Let us know your thoughts! :)
#gamedev #indiedev #devlog 

Music: Serenade of Water by Mikel https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b4eH8tQORX8&ab_channel=Mikel
